quote.summary: Greentown Service Group Co Ltd is a company mainly principally in providing property services. The Company also engages in community living services, consulting services, technology services, and other businesses. The property services provide a range of property management services, such as security, cleaning, gardening, and repair and maintenance services. The consulting services are provided in project planning, design management, construction management and marketing management consulting services during the design and development stages and display unit management services, management consulting services, and others. The community living services mainly include community products and services, home living services, community space services, property asset management services, and cultural and educational services. The technology services provide intelligent, inclusive, and affordable integrated solutions. The Other business is mainly investment properties.
